<h1>Problem 2127 - Folklore, AC</h1>
<h2 class='difficulty'>Difficulty: 9</h2>
<p>There is an alphabet with 2 letters and 100 words. It is known that if you write any finite combination of the 100 words in a row, it can be uniquely determined what words were written, and in what order. What is the minimal sum of the lengths of the words?</p>
